<function>

access:   public

name: mimeType

param: mixed, $value

param: array, $allowed, NULL

param: bool, $blank, false

return: bool

</function>

Validate that a value is formatted as a MIME type.

* Parameters:

 * mixed //$value//: The value to validate.

 * array //$allowed//: The MIME type must be one of these allowed values; if null, then all values are allowed.

 * bool //$blank//: Allow blank values to be valid.

* Returns bool: True if valid, false if not.